            "body": "Strawman API proposal:\r\n\r\n```javascript\r\n\r\nbot.outgoingPluginChannels.register('foo', 'bar', 'baz', ...); // send REGISTER foo\\0bar\\0baz\r\nbot.outgoingPluginChannels.emit('foo', raw_payload); // send foo <raw_payload>\r\nbot.outgoingPluginChannels.unregister('foo'); // send UNREGISTER foo\r\n\r\nbot.incomingPluginChannels.on('quux', function(raw_payload) {\r\n  // other side sent us a plugin channel message, app can now decode it\r\n});\r\n// optionally listen for channel registrations/unregistrations from other side\r\nbot.incomingPluginChannels.onRegister(function(channelNameList) {}); // ['foo', 'bar', 'baz']\r\nbot.incomingPluginChannels.onUnregister(function(channelNameList) {}); // ['foo']\r\n// (.on('REGISTER', ...) would give raw_payload='foo\\0bar\\0baz'), etc.\r\n```",
